Time Team (History Documentary)
Time - 17:45 - 18:45 (1 hour long)
When - Sunday 30th March on Channel 4
Hunting King Harold: Portskewett, South Wales.
The intriguingly named Harold&#039;s Field in South Wales is the latest destination for Time Team. Local legend has it that King Harold built a hunting lodge there the year before he lost the Battle of Hastings. First impressions are encouraging. The field is a mass of big earthworks and historical documents do record Harold building a lodge somewhere round the village of Portskewett.
